dct_title_s: Pascaert vande ZUYD ZEE en een gedeelte van BRASIL Van Ilhas de Ladronos tot R. de la Plata
dct_description_sm: Robijn's 1683 map entitled "Wassende graadt kaert vande Groote, Zuyd, Zee..." is nearly identical.
California as an island on second Sanson model, with indented northern coast and coastal place names.
Wagner 443; Tooley 45; Leighly 71; Koeman, IV, Keu3A(28),Keu5(40),Keu7(37),Keu8(37),Keu10(39), Keu13(38),Keu18(37),Keu19(40),Keu20B(148),Keu28(182),Keu123A(23),Keu123D(23); Koeman, IV,page395.
"Staten Landt" to far southwest; "Compagnies Land" to far northwest, with incomplete outline of each. Three drawings of sailing ships on the Pacific.
In: De groote nieuwe vermeerderde Zee-Atlas ofte water-werelt, 1680. Reissued in 1681,1682,1683,1684,1685,1692,1694, and 1695.
In: De nieuwe groote lightende Zee-Fakkel, Part V, 1683. Reissued in 1687.
by Ioannes van Keulen aen de Nieuwe brugh in de Gekroonde Lootsman Met Priviligie voor 15 Laar.
